discriminate.content:
differ和vary都有“不同，相异”的意思，differ指两者之间有不同点，或与某人意见不统一，如
Chinese differs from English in this respect.
在这方面汉语不同于英语。
vary指一组类似的事物在大小、形状等方面有别，如
Average test scores vary from class to class.
各班的平均测验成绩不同。

sents.en: These suggestions which were put forward in the environmental conference vary in influence and importance.
sents.zh: 在环保会议上提出的这些建议在影响力和重要性上都存在着差异。

sents.en: These opinions will change with time, and vary from place to place.
sents.zh: 这些观点会根据时间和地点的不同而改变。

sents.en: As opinions vary on that point, no decision can be reached.
sents.zh: 在那一点上，大家意见纷纷，莫衷一是。
